Project Overview
Royal Stay is a modern, responsive hotel booking website designed to provide users with an intuitive interface for browsing room options, checking availability, and completing reservations. The platform features a clean design with dynamic pricing calculations and a seamless booking experience.

Features
Responsive design optimized for all devices

Interactive booking widget with date selection

Dynamic pricing based on room type, occupancy, and dates

Room comparison with detailed amenities

Secure booking modal with payment processing simulation

Indian pricing format with rupee symbol

Technology Stack
Frontend: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (ES6+)

Icons: Font Awesome 6.4.0

Images: Unsplash (royalty-free)

No external dependencies - completely self-contained

Run command:Open live sever